{
  "description": "This image captures a stunning coastal view where clear turquoise water meets rocky terrain. The water is incredibly transparent, revealing a seabed composed of smooth, rounded stones and pebbles in various shades of grey, brown, and white. The sunlight creates shimmering patterns on the water's surface and illuminates the rocks below, highlighting their texture and color. The foreground features rugged, dry, beige-colored rocks, suggesting a Mediterranean or arid environment. There's a clear transition from the dry land to the submerged stones, and the deeper water appears a vibrant deep blue. The composition emphasizes the natural beauty and clarity of the coastal landscape.",
